## --- Visual Studio / .NET --- ##
# This catches bin/obj in both ElementFinder.Core and Example Site
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## --- Umbraco 17 Specific (Example Site) --- ##
# Ignore runtime data and logs
**/umbraco/Data/TEMP/
**/umbraco/Logs/
# Ignore local SQLite databases
**/umbraco/Data/*.sqlite.db*
**/umbraco/Data/*.sqlite-wal
**/umbraco/Data/*.sqlite-shm
# Ignore auto-generated models (if using ModelsBuilder in Live mode)
**/umbraco/models/*.generated.cs

## --- Lit / Vite Package (package folder) --- ##
# Ignore dependencies and build artifacts
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
# Ignore Vite/TS build logs
*.tsbuildinfo
.eslintcache

## --- Misc / OS --- ##
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.env
.env.local